p=\"n\" name=\"num 6\">\nThe match was not played, because Esteghlal refused to do it. [[Islamic Republic of Iran Football Federation|Football Federation]] declared the match 3\u20130 in favor of Persepolis.\n</ref>\n}}\n\n== References ==\n\n* [https://www.ilna.news/%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%B4-%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%B2%D8%B4%DB%8C-7/317685-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AE%DA%86%D9%87-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D9%87%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D9%87%D9%85%DA%86%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%88%DB%8C-%D8%A2%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D9%87%D8%A7 \u062a\u0627\u0631\u06cc\u062e\u0686\u0647 \u06a9\u0627\u0645\u0644 91 \u062f\u0631\u0628\u06cc \u0633\u0631\u062e\u0627\u0628\u06cc\u200c\u0647\u0627]\n* [https://www.mashreghnews.ir/news/277441/%D9%87%D9%85%D9%87-%DA%AF%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D9%88-%D8%B1%DA%A9%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%AF-%D8%B9%D8%AC%DB%8C%D8%A8-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3-%D8%AC%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%84 \u0647\u0645\u0647 \u06af\u0644\u0632\u0646\u0627\u0646 \u062f\u0631\u0628\u06cc]\n<references />\n\n== External links ==\n\n* [https://www.fifa.com/news/the-battle-tehran-1165699 The battle of Tehran], [[FIFA]]\n* [https://www.asriran.com/fa/news/199225/%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AC-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%AA%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%A2%D8%BA%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AA%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B2 List of Tehran Derby matches] (In [[Persian language|Persian]])\n\n[[Category:Football derbies in Iran]]\n[[Category:Persepolis F.C. matches]]\n[[Category:Esteghlal F.C.]]\n", "text_old": "This is a list of all matches contested between the two prominent [[Tehran]] [[Football club|clubs]] [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]] and [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]], a fixture known as '''''Tehran Derby'''''.\n\n== Iranian League (Persian Gulf Pro League) ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!Derby No.\n! width=\"2\" |Seas