89\n| align=\"left\" |Tehran Province League\n| align=\"left\" |Persepolis\n| bgcolor=\"F00000\" |<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''1\u20130'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| align=\"left\" |<small>Abedian 18'</small>\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n|-\n|34\n| align=\"left\" |1990\u201391\n| align=\"left\" |18-01-1991\n| align=\"left\" |Tehran Province League\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| bgcolor=\"808080\" |<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''1\u20131'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Persepolis\n| align=\"left\" |<small>[[Shahrokh Bayani|Bayani]] 62' (pen.)</small>\n| align=\"left\" |<small>[[Farshad Pious|Pious]] 75'</small>\n|-\n|35\n| align=\"left\" |1991\u201392\n| align=\"left\" |24-01-1992\n| align=\"left\" |Tehran Province League\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| bgcolor=\"808080\" |<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''0\u20130'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Persepolis\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n|-\n|38\n| align=\"left\" |1992\u201393\n| align=\"left\" |01-01-1993\n| align=\"left\" |Tehran Super Cup (qualifications for [[1993\u201394 Azadegan League]])\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| bgcolor=\"808080\" |<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''0\u20130'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Persepolis\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n|}\n|}\n</div>\n\n== Friendlies and Exhibitions ==\n\n<div style=\"font-size:100%\">\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!Derby No.\n! width=\"6%\" |Year\n!Date(dd-mm-yyyy)\n!Competition\n!Home team\n!Score\n!Away team\n!Home goal scorers\n!Away goal scorers\n! width=\"8%\" |Winner\n|-\n|1\n| align=\"left\" |1968\n| align=\"left\" |05-04-1968\n|Friendly\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| bgcolor=\"808080\" |<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''0\u20130'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Persepolis\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n| align=\"left\" |\u2013\n| align=\"left\" |'''None'''\n|-\n|2\n| align=\"left\" |1968\n| align=\"left\" |