\">'''2\u20132'''</span></center>\n| align=\"left\" |Esteghlal\n| align=\"left\" |<small>[[Hadi Norouzi|Norouzi]] 7' (pen.), 46'</small>\n| align=\"left\" |<small>[[Arash Borhani|Borhani]] 32', [[Hanif Omranzadeh|Omranzadeh]] 70'</small>\n| align=\"left\" |'''None'''\n|}\n\n== Summary of all matches ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|'''Esteghlal wins'''\n|'''26'''\n|-\n|'''Persepolis wins'''\n|'''24'''\n|-\n|'''Draws'''\n|'''42'''\n|-\n|'''Esteghlal goals'''\n|'''85'''\n|-\n|'''Persepolis goals'''\n|'''89'''\n|-\n|'''Total matches'''\n|'''92'''\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{Reflist| group=\"n\"|30em| refs =\n<ref group=\"n\" name=\"num\">\nThe original match was 1\u20130 until 82' when Persepolis players ground out. [[Islamic Republic of Iran Football Federation|Football Federation]] declared the match 3\u20130 in favor of Esteghlal.\n</ref>\n\n<ref group=\"n\" name=\"num 2\">\nThe original match was 1\u20131 until 75' when Persepolis players ground out. [[Islamic Republic of Iran Football Federation|Football Federation]] declared the match 3\u20130 in favor of Esteghlal.\n</ref>\n\n<ref group=\"n\" name=\"num 4\">\nThe original match was 2\u20132 until 89' when Persepolis fans stormed into the ground. [[Islamic Republic of Iran Football Federation|Football Federation]] declared the match 3\u20130 in favor of Esteghlal.\n</ref>\n\n<ref group=\"n\" name=\"num 6\">\nThe match was not played, because Esteghlal refused to do it. [[Islamic Republic of Iran Football Federation|Football Federation]] declared the match 3\u20130 in favor of Persepolis.\n</ref>\n}}\n\n== References ==\n\n* [https://www.ilna.news/%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%B4-%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%B2%D8%B4%DB%8C-7/317685-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AE%DA%86%D9%87-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D9%87%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D9%87%D9%85%DA%86%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%88%DB%8C-%D8%A2%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D9%87%D8%A7 \u062a\u0627\u0631\u06cc\u062e\u0686\